                    <span>This is a very exciting video about the origin, history, developments, success and failures of the Internet. It has good detail in the topics and companies that refers, but it does not touch every important(historical level) company in the net.  Perhaps less time for "excite" and jokes, and more time to relevant companies and phenomena.</span>
                  
