                    <span>This is a nice, broad overview of the history of the internet. I found it easy to watch - it kept my attention. The video includes numerous segmented interviews with key people involved in this history. I found these interviews to be most interesting. I got a feel for the personalities - for their visions, their successes, their challenges.<p>The video has three 1 hour tapes. There is also a book by the same name that was prepared based on the video.</span>
                  
              
